# CQ2: Which obligations apply to providers of high-risk AI systems? (Articles 9-15 and 72)
PREFIX euai: <https://zhaoxing-li.github.io/eu-ai-act-ontology#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?obligation ?label ?article WHERE {
  ?obligation euai:imposedOn euai:Provider ;
              euai:appliesToSystem euai:HighRiskAISystem ;
              rdfs:label ?label ;
              euai:hasArticleReference ?article .
}
ORDER BY ?article
